  <h2>Maternity Measuring Guide</h2>
  <p>Matalan maternity collection is available in sizes 8-18. All our maternity styles are sized according
    to your pre-pregnancy size with natural ease added to garments for your comfort during pregnancy.
  </p>
  <p>
    <strong>Maternity Trousers, Skirts and Shorts fit Guide</strong>
  </p>
  <p>For all our trousers, skirts and shorts a variety of stretch and supporting panels are used to ensure
    maximum comfort. Each and every style is designed around your new curves and growing bump during
    pregnancy. The use of elasticated stretchy fabrics that contain elastane ensure the fabric will grow
    with you through all your stages of pregnancy.</p>
  <p>
    <strong>Matalan Fit - Maternity Jeans</strong>
  </p>
  <p>Maternity jeans are often worn before and for a while after the birth of your baby. We always carefully
    consider the styling of our jeans as we look for softer washes in our denims keeping comfort our
    main focus whilst offering fashionable styling. We offer various choices of waistband styling to
    accommodate&nbsp;and flatter your shape and growing bump.</p>
